FBIS3-15685 "drsov046_m_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-046 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Mar 1994 Tajikistan General on Absence of Casualties in 4 Months LD0803210194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1930 GMT 8 Mar 94 LD0803210194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the "Slavyanka" program of the Russian Defense Ministry] [Text] Addressing servicemen's mothers, Colonel General Boris Pyankov, commander of the collective peacekeeping forces of the CIS in Tajikistan, says that: [Begin Pyankov recording] Fortunately, during the four months that these peacekeeping forces have been functioning there have been no combat losses in their units; we did not lose a single person and during this entire time one serviceman was slightly injured". [end recording] He then goes on to thank the mothers for sending their sons to Tajikistan and wishes a safe return home for every mother's son.
